trans-unit.source: Imports WSDL-based policies and contracts about privacy notices into descriptions of the binding elements that can implement these policies for the service.
trans-unit.target: WSDL 架構原則和有關隱私權注意事項的合約匯入繫結項目可實作這些原則的服務的說明中。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PrivacyNoticeBindingElementImporter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新執行個體<xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PrivacyNoticeBindingElementImporter"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: Imports custom policy assertions for privacy notices and adds the binding elements that implement the policy.
trans-unit.target: 匯入隱私權注意事項的自訂原則判斷提示，並新增實作原則的繫結項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataImporter"></xref> that imports the metadata information.

The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext"></xref> object that contains the policy assertions that can be imported and the collections of binding elements to which custom binding elements that implement the encoding policy can be added.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Description.PolicyConversionContext"> </xref>物件，其中包含可以匯入的原則判斷提示，以及繫結項目可以加入實作編碼原則的自訂繫結項目集合。
